Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Claudsdale's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:14.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's mean Ponyville is next up to winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're doing awesome, everypony, keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We need those leaves on those trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:35.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Once we get autumn cleared away, it'll be "hello, winter"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Was that a yawn I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:48.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How can you be tired when the most exciting time of the year is right around the corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:51.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And don't forget the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:54.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Our first winter together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:03.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Once those ponies bring in the big fat clouds full of snowflakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,we'll have a ton of snow for our extreme sledding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:19.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And over there, we can play horse hockey, with no shoulder or arm pads!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everything's looking great, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:34.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Almost everything. Does Tank look alright to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, he does seem to be moving a little slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:41.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:44.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And he looks kind of sleepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…just like he always does!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:50.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ha ha, I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:48.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I suppose his heartbeat could be a teensy-weensy-eensy bit slower than usual…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, so give him a vitamin or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think he needs that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're just staying up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Too many Daring Do stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, what's wrong with him, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Nothing! He's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,He's just going to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You do realize he's not a bear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:20.63,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,When the weather grows cold and less food is available,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:24.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,many animals hibernate to conserve energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:29.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's like taking a really long nap during winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and then they wake up in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:34.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And see? Even tortoises do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, Tank will leave and dig into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:46.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But don't worry. He'll reappear when the spring sun warms the ground back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on! Tortoises don't hibernate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Somepony put that picture in there as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well then your book must be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:01.35,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Tank needs to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:05.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's healthy for him, just like sleeping is healthy for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:09.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What-ever. Okay, thanks. Come on, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.25,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:19.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,To get a second opinion from a real reptile expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:24.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,I told you, Rainbow Dash, I'm a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on! You're practically twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:34.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But if you don't have to hibernate, why should Tank?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,Because he's a tortoise, and I'm a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Same family though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Look, if Fluttershy says tortoises hibernate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,then I guarantee tortoises hiber-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:50.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what would you know?! You're a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Nopony knows you like I do, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:59.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,All you need is some hard work to get the old blood pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,These things are heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:19.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Chock full of snowflakes! We're gonna have such a killer time in the snow, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:32.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,look at the cute wittle Tankie, all snuggly-wuggly, getting ready to hibern—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't say that word!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Which one? "Snuggly"? "Wuggly"? "Tankie"? "Hibernate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I was just saying how cute he—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If you think hiber…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:46.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,- you know, that napping thing – is so cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:50.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,why don't you go do it?! Somewhere far away from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie and I are just having a conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:04.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look, Rainbow Dash, we all know how upset you are about Tank hiber—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Shhhh! Don't say that word! That's what started this all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We all know how upset you are about Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't take your anger out on your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Who said anything about anger?! I didn't say anything about anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm not upset! And I am not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Do I look angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tank! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I need you bright-eyed and bushy-tailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.57,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not sleepy-eyed and scaly-tailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Which is exactly what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:39.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But get up anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You can't hiber… you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What about all the primo things we're gonna do together this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:55.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Building snow ponies, starting snowball fights, sipping hot cider by the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna do those things with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Think, Rainbow Dash, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Tank's only hibernating because it's cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:17.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd rather have him awake in the heat than asleep in the cold…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I just have to stop winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,So where do these clouds go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Over by Clear Skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But there's clear skies everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:37.16,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yo, Clear Skies right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But there's clear skies over there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That's Open Skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There's open skies everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:45.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm not everywhere, I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:50.21,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Wait, so you're Open Skies, and you're Clear Skies, then what's all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.21,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Open clear skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.43,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did fluffy clouds go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:58.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Fluffy Clouds is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Stopping winter is gonna be a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:22.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,When life gives you lemons \N You can make lemonade
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:29.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But life gave me Tank here \N And my choice has long been made
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:37.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No winter will come to Ponyville \N I'll do it on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:44.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I will keep you by my side \N So I will not be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:51.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I'll fly, and I'll fly \N Until the end of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:58.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So I'll be the one who doesn't \N Have to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:05.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll clear the skies forever \N So we won't be apart
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:12.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll keep the weather warm for you \N And the winter will never start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:24.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Weather-makers Pegasi \N You make the seasons in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:31.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sabotage you \N But you see, I've got to try
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:38.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No winter can come here now \N I'll keep the warmth and the sun somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:45.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, ponies, this has to be \N For I need my friend and he needs me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:52.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know it's wrong, but what does it matter? \N 'Cause nothing's gonna stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:59.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll change it all, it's only the weather \N And nopony's gonna bring me down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:05.94,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll keep the sunlight shining free
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:12.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I'll bust the clouds apart so you can stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:18.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I'll fly, and I'll fly \N Until the end of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:25.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So I'll be the one who doesn't \N Have to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:33.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll clear the skies forever \N So we won't be apart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:42.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll keep the weather warm for you \N And the winter will never start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Here comes the next shipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Move those clouds over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:09.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,For every hoof step back, they go three hoof steps forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.63,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's it, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If I can't stop winter in Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,maybe I can stop it at the source!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Lunch hour. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The winter lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're in, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:47.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now we just gotta figure out a way to shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:49.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sabotage snowflakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:52.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think we're gotta go bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:11.91,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We could get rid of these clouds, but that's still not big enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Slam dunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,With no water they can't make clouds or snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They can't make winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I hate to do this to those weather ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:31.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but desperate times call for desperate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oopsie! Looks like these were a little loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:42.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And there goes winter… down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:31.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Let's get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:57.84,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in the name of Celestia is going on up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Winter is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You okay, Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, are you allright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The poor thing looks so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we {\i1}can{\i0} do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Buck up, sugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You just ain't yourself these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How can I say this tactfully…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You've lost your sparkle, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:37.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:38.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You've become…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.37,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,a party pooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I said whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:49.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're here to cheer me up or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:57.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, your winter is going to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,petless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:15.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Whatever did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:19.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Because she'll never get past this until she lets it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.74,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Tank will come back in a few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Months?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:43.54,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:46.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nice going, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:51.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How do we get her to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,She's got to be about done by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Can't be too much left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:15.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor, poor thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:20.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to see Fluttershy cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's just heartwrenching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Look, everypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know how hard it is to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:41.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm mostly sad because you're {\i1}not{\i0} sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What?! Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What about Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Applejack cries on the inside, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:51.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You think she's done, or just getting a third wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Really, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I'd do without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Or him…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tank, I'm sure gonna miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we're starting winter with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The fun's come early!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.05,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You think we could mess up winter every year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's way less work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think Rainbow Dash could handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:03.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Riding that entire season from Cloudsdale to Ponyville was pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:09.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I thought you guys might like to say goodbye to Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:11.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He's ready to hibernate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're using the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She is using the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:20.83,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And when Tank finishes hibernating, I'm gonna throw him the biggest welcome home party ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:21.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Or wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Should it be a "welcome above ground" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Or a "happy wake up" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:28.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Maybe an "it's about time" party?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:31.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I'll design him a very special suit just for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Whichever one it ends up being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feeling a little better, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, you really wanna do this hibernating thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Happy winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See you later, little feller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Have a good sleep, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Tank! We'll miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:13.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, ready for some winter fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hang here and read to him a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That little guy can never get to sleep without a bedtime story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
